Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Už se nudím. Pojďme to zklidit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrý nápad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:04.27,KopieNápis,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs120\frz270\pos(495,235)}_____
